sensortoolkit._ingest.sensor_import.Ingest_Example_Make_Model¶

Ingest_Example_Make_Model(cwd)[source]¶

Ingestion module for an example sensor dataset.

Recorded sensor data are imported and headers are converted into a standard format for analysis.

Parameters

cwd (str) – The full path to the sensor data file

Returns

A dataframe containing sensor data that

has been converted into standardized syntax

Return type

df (Pandas DataFrame object)
